 seinem Tafelservice als auch aus Kirchen- und Innungssilber Klippen schlagen. M\u00f6glicherweise sind die goldenen Exemplare erst sp\u00e4ter als Erinnerungsst\u00fccke gepr\u00e4gt worden und nur die Bleim\u00fcnzen w\u00e4hrend der Belagerung. Der auf den M\u00fcnzen angegebene 9. Mai bezeichnet den Tag der Einschlie\u00dfung Braunaus.","period":{"ikmk_period_id":"13","name_de":"Barock","name_en":"Baroque","description_de":"Kunst bzw- Stilperiode, welche mit regional unterschiedlichen Entwicklungen die Zeit vom Ende des 16. Jahrhunderts ist ca. 1730 umfasst. Teilweise wird der Rokoko (bis ca. 1770) ihr auch zugerechnet.","description_en":"Art period with a regionally varying developement in chronological terms roughly from the end of the 16th century to c. 1730. Sometimes the following period Rococo (to c. 1770) is considered a late form of Baroque.","concept_id":"http:\/\/vocab.getty.edu\/aat\/300021147","ndp_uri":"https:\/\/ikmk.smb.museum\/ndp\/period\/13"},"year_start":"1743","year_end":"1743","date_verbal":"1743","year_islam":"0","manufacturing":[{"ikmk_manufacturing_id":"21","manufacturing_name_de":"gepr\u00e4gt","manufacturing_name_en":"struck","nomisma_id":"http:\/\/nomisma.org\/id\/struck","ndp_uri":"https:\/\/ikmk.smb.museum\/ndp\/manufacture\/21"}],"linked_persons_corporations":{"50":{"ikmk_type_id":"50","type_name_de":"Vorbesitzer","type_name_en":"previous Owner","type_nomisma_id":"","type_concept_id":"http:\/\/d-nb.info\/gnd\/4447273-0","ndp_id":"https:\/\/ikmk.smb.museum\/ndp\/type_for_person_and_corporation\/50","items":{"5474":{"ikmk_person_id":"5474","title_de":null,"first_name_de":"Benoni","last_name_de":"Friedl\u00e4nder","vitalDates":"04.06.1773 - 17.02.1858","title_en":null,"first_name_en":"Benoni","last_name_en":"Friedl\u00e4nder","corporation":"0","lod":{"https:\/\/d-nb.info\/gnd\/116796634":"https:\/\/d-nb.info\/gnd\/116796634","https:\/\/viaf.org\/viaf\/40139014":"https:\/\/viaf.org\/viaf\/40139014","https:\/\/www.wikidata.org\/wiki\/Q81